---- Changes since 1.6 ----
Password protection of a domain's CGI subdirectories can now be added.
---- Changes since 1.8 ----
Support adding protection to directories with an existing .htaccess file, and removing it without deleting the file.
---- Changes since 2.1 ----
Added a button for find protected directories under a virtual server's home, so that manually added .htaccess files can be managed.
